<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Restaurant Reviews</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .header {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .top-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .btn-secondary { background: #6c757d; }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background: #545b62; }
        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 30px 0 15px 0;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        p {
            color: #495057;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .team-section {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        .team-member {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .team-member:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .member-avatar {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            margin: 0 auto 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .member-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .member-role {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .member-bio {
            color: #495057;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }
        .feature-list li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .feature-list li:before {
            content: "✓";
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .mission-statement {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .mission-statement h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .stat-item {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .stat-label {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="top-bar">
                <h1>About Us</h1>
                <div>
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary">← Back to Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/" class="btn" style="margin-left: 10px;">Home</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>Learn more about our mission, team, and the story behind Restaurant Reviews.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="mission-statement">
                <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>To connect food lovers with authentic dining experiences through honest reviews, 
                trusted recommendations, and a community-driven platform that celebrates culinary excellence.</p>
            </div>

            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Restaurant Reviews was born from a simple idea: dining decisions should be based on 
            authentic experiences, not just marketing. In a world filled with endless restaurant choices, 
            we wanted to create a platform where real people share real experiences.</p>
            <p>What started as a small project for food enthusiasts has grown into a vibrant community 
            of thousands who trust our platform to discover their next favorite restaurant, share their 
            culinary adventures, and connect with fellow food lovers.</p>

            <h2>What We Offer</h2>
            <ul class="feature-list">
                <li>Authentic reviews from real customers</li>
                <li>Detailed restaurant information and photos</li>
                <li>Advanced search and filtering options</li>
                <li>Personalized recommendations</li>
                <li>User-friendly rating system</li>
                <li>Community engagement features</li>
                <li>Mobile-responsive design</li>
                <li>Secure and transparent platform</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">200+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Restaurants</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">1000+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Reviews</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">500+</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Active Users</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">4.8</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Average Rating</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
            <div class="team-section">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <div class="member-avatar">S</div>
                    <div class="member-name">Shirish</div>
                    <div class="member-role">Frontend Lead & UI/UX Designer</div>
                    <div class="member-bio">Passionate about creating beautiful, intuitive interfaces that enhance user experience. Brings designs to life with modern web technologies.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <div class="member-avatar">P</div>
                    <div class="member-name">Poorva</div>
                    <div class="member-role">Backend Lead & Database Manager</div>
                    <div class="member-bio">Expert in database architecture and server-side development. Ensures our platform is robust, scalable, and efficient.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <div class="member-avatar">S</div>
                    <div class="member-name">Shreya</div>
                    <div class="member-role">Project Coordinator & Full-Stack Developer</div>
                    <div class="member-bio">Orchestrates team collaboration and bridges frontend-backend development. Focuses on seamless integration and project delivery.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <p><strong>Authenticity:</strong> We believe in honest, unbiased reviews from real customers.</p>
            <p><strong>Community:</strong> We foster a supportive environment where food lovers can connect and share.</p>
            <p><strong>Quality:</strong> We're committed to maintaining high standards for reviews and restaurant information.</p>
            <p><strong>Innovation:</strong> We continuously improve our platform to better serve our community.</p>
            <p><strong>Transparency:</strong> We're open about how our platform works and how we handle data.</p>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 30px; border-top: 2px solid #e9ecef;">
                <p>Thank you for being part of our community! Together, we're making dining decisions easier and more enjoyable.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn" style="margin-top: 20px;">Get in Touch</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>